 target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importan=
t; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-st=
yle: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> talked</a> a few <a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26954045.260607/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb2=
1iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDMtMDIvcnVzc2lhLXMtZmluYW5jZXMtY=
XJlLWNsb3NpbmctdXA_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDMwODIyX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFp=
