world=E2=80=99s lowest-cost building material.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px =
0;">By combining automation with low material costs, we can build an arbitr=
arily large structure at a much lower cost than stone or concrete.</p><p st=
yle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The RealPyramidScheme DAO will decide collectively =
on the design and location of the pyramid. The more we raise, the bigger it=
